hpnicft1Table.name: hpnicft1Table
hpnicft1Table.description: A list of T1 interface entries.

hpnicft1Entry.name: hpnicft1Entry
hpnicft1Entry.description: This entry contains T1 interface management information.

HpnicfT1TimeSlot.name: HpnicfT1TimeSlot
HpnicfT1TimeSlot.description: Each octet within this value specifies a set of time slots, with the first octet specifying time slot 1 through 8, the second octet specifying time slots 9 through 16, etc. Within each octet, the most significant bit represents the highest numbered time slot, and the least significant bit represents the lowest numbered time slot. Thus, each time slot of the T1 is represented by a single bit within the value of this object. If that bit has a value of '1' then that time slot is included in the set of time slots; the time slot is not included if its bit has a value of '0'.

hpnicft1PriSetTimeSlot.name: hpnicft1PriSetTimeSlot
hpnicft1PriSetTimeSlot.description: This is a bit-map of PRI time slots used on the T1 interface. It needs to administratively shut down the D channel of the T1 interface before cancelling PRI time slots.
